                <h2>Who?  What?  Why?</h2>
                <p>Greetings to you! So, who am I? My name is Elizabeth, I was born in England and I am a photographer. When I was 5 years old, my parents made a fateful gift. They handed me my first camera and I've been shooting ever since. What else do you need to know about me? Perhaps the fact that I fell in love. With people. With nature. With animals. With art. Every day I see beauty and it captures me. I know for sure that there is nothing more exciting and fascinating than the shutter release of the camera. This is the magic that stops time, the magic of creating a picture from the moment of life. Magic available to everyone. What am I doing? If it is short - art. Why am I doing this? I love this and this loves me. Every day is filled with new faces and stories, places, and sensations. And I want to share it with everyone. I want people to be able to see, feel, and enjoy this world through my work.</p>
            </div>
                
